data.description: East facing, 3+ bedroom Raised Ranch on a dead-end street. Lower level features a family room, full bath, laundry room and a fourth bedroom/office. In the upper main level, you'll find the kitchen with eat-in dining, tiled floors and access to the side yard. Large living room with coat closet, the three main bedrooms and main hall bath finish out the main level. Attached, tuck-under one-car garage. This property sits on just under half an acre lot, close to schools, MUM campus and other amenities. New Roof and gutters in July 2023.
